original_title: The Rascal Joins the Wrestling Team
overview: Brandon Weber is back as the irascible Rascal, along with all the non-sexual extras that give the Rascal Features their charm; Sharon Kane, Tony Fontana, Mark Jensen, Desiree DeBaum, and Jack O'Neill. If a YOUNG MAN ALERT! is something you're on the look out for, look out for THE RASCAL JOINS THE WRESTLING TEAM.
tagline: Catalina presents the second release in our hugely popular Freshman Features Series of 18-22 year old spunksters; THE RASCAL JOINS THE WRESTLING TEAM.
title: The Rascal Joins the Wrestling Team
